        "pricingRisks": [
          "CRITICAL INDUSTRY MISMATCH: This RFP seeks a mature, hosted data warehouse and BI/analytics platform product (similar to PowerSchool Analytics, Tableau, Qlik, or Schoolzilla). HORUSTECH is a custom software development firm, not a product vendor with an existing K-12 data warehouse/BI SaaS platform.",
